    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2267930/extras/f549cc7689c3f66bfe4b2a3e3a01c2c6.poster.avif?t=1728531093\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2267930/extras/f549cc7689c3f66bfe4b2a3e3a01c2c6.webm?t=1728531093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2267930/extras/f549cc7689c3f66bfe4b2a3e3a01c2c6.mp4?t=1728531093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>MITE, 是一款以日本民间传说和地区流行历史为基础的第三人称恐怖游戏...在地区最闹鬼的森林中夜晚被追逐的恐怖中，体验被一只奇怪的妖怪追逐的恐怖，只要你不看它，它就会缠着你。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2267930/extras/62ee0fa2cdd50e11ff86d09aa3f320a4.avif?t=1728531093\" width=600 height=74 /></span><br><br>【第一章】<br>在这个地区最神秘的森林中，一个失去妻子和儿子的徒步旅行者，一个夜晚不应该待在的森林中，必须找到他的伴侣和儿子...同时被一只奇怪的生物追逐，只要你不看它，它就会慢慢接近...走路时要小心不要摔倒...因为如果你不看它...也许当你抬头时，你会面对面地看到它，带上你的家人逃离森林，尽量不要再回去。<br><br>【第二章（不可用）】<br>在第二章中，MITE将成为被追捕的对象，神父塔基和两名警察将追捕他，他们会结束MITE吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2267930/extras/5b9524781c35a9ba83fc91cfd8587da3.poster.avif?t=1728531093\" width=600 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2267930/extras/5b9524781c35a9ba83fc91cfd8587da3.webm?t=1728531093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2267930/extras/5b9524781c35a9ba83fc91cfd8587da3.mp4?t=1728531093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2267930/extras/54bada6ddff89b7a6b71fbc70d547d75.avif?t=1728531093\" width=600 height=76 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[]<strong>恐惧体验：</strong> 体验在充满灵魂和日本妖怪的森林中行走的恐怖。[]<strong>探索：</strong> 在森林中漫游，小心行走，尽量不要停下来长时间看着奇怪的灵魂...否则它会靠近你。[]<strong>类型：</strong> 这款游戏属于恐怖叙事类型，专为恐怖电影爱好者设计。[]<strong>定向：</strong> 在没有指南针的森林中，最困难的是找到自己的方向，请自己找到路，你的家人正在等你。<li><strong>无存档：</strong> 由于其简单性，这款游戏是一次通过的，但这并不是一件容易的事情。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2267930/extras/27070a5d206eeb941b83e69172d77260.poster.avif?t=1728531093\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2267930/extras/27070a5d206eeb941b83e69172d77260.webm?t=1728531093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2267930/extras/27070a5d206eeb941b83e69172d77260.mp4?t=1728531093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2267930/extras/8486d71083cdc7cd6b76558220a36348.avif?t=1728531093\" width=600 height=74 /></span><br><br>我们的工作室专注于恐怖游戏，并经常以日本民间传说和神话作为灵感来源。<br>在Kanashi工作室，我们研究定价，并为所有玩家设定了合理的<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2267930/extras/2d20a0b792fc43cfb56cfa373a2edbc4.webp?t=1728531093\" width=52 height=107 /></span>",
